    "7300201": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Withering Zone that needs to be cleaned up",
        "Step": "You and Paimon put in a good amount of hard work to sort your stories into a version that the children might find interesting. Thankfully, they like your stories. Although they don't seem to have told the truth about the mysterious creatures, this isn't the time to go into detail. Now, go with Rana to clear out some Withering Zones. You're doing this so the children of Vimara Village can play safely, after all.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Whew, it's nice to have the chance to do something. This should help with our problem a little."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#Besides, watching you fight made me realize that I still have a lot to learn, {NICKNAME}! Like footwork... and timing too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "An experienced traveler like you is just... absolutely amazing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thanks."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Piece of cake."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon has me on a strict training regimen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Heh, well, we're always improving together as companions!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#Thank you so much, really. That reminds me, how's your condition, {NICKNAME}? After taking care of so many Withering Zones, do you feel dizzy or nauseous or anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nothing I can't handle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just a little tired."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ugh... I think I'm dying."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Eh? II see, lie down, quickly! I'll go get help..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hey! Don't make jokes like that, {NICKNAME}! You'll worry Rana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just kidding, sorry about that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I actually feel completely fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "That's good... You've done so much. Goodness, I feel so much better now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Let's take a break! One of our forest patrol campsites isn't far from here. It should have equipment and supplies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm actually not that tired..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yay, let's go camping!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Camping! That sounds fun!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Then off we go! It's just ahead."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
