    "7300205": {
        "Desc": "Go to the area where the Spinocrocodiles are active",
        "Step": "The Withering Zones Rana marked on the map have been cleared out. According to Rana, the recent spike in Spinocrocodile activity was caused by the Withering, as it made them especially violent. So, besides the danger they pose to the children, they will affect the ecosystem of the forest too. Now, head over to the area where Spinocrocodiles are active and drive them away.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#Besides firewood, we have sufficient supplies of everything else here... Ah, {NICKNAME}, you're back! Have you collected enough firewood?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "It's fine, leave it to me. Just stay here and rest up! Let me just clean up here and I'll go right away!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let me do it. It won't take long."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I just wanted to tell you that I'm going now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Alright. Thanks."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7300220": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Rana",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#Oh, {NICKNAME}, you're back! I was so worried..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "I was afraid you and Paimon had run off... or worse, that those alligators from before came back for revenge and hauled you both away!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are alligators really that scary!? We saw that you were sleeping, so we went to take care of some other things..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Sorry, I didn't even realize that I had fallen asleep, hehe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You can sleep even while sitting upright..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You must have been exhausted before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Not really, I just ate a lot and was feeling so relaxed that I just..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Ahem! Here's a little Forest Watcher trivia for you: When searching for missing people in the forest, we make sure to feed them something that's easy to digest when we find them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Digestion consumes stamina. That's why you feel sleepy easily after eating. Or at least, that's what the Akademiya researchers say."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, Paimon, have you rested? You worked so hard yesterday..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We slept like babies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No need, I feel great."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! Don't worry about us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Are you sure? Okay then... Thank you so much for yesterday. I feel much better now that you're here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Heh, you can count on {NICKNAME}! Is there any work left to do today, Rana?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Let me see... I think we're just about done here, let's head back to Vimara Village! We can check in on the situation on our way back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, let's go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
