    "7300212": {
        "Desc": "Light the campfire",
        "Step": "The Forest Watchers seem to have a tradition when camping: It should be the most esteemed person in the group who lights the campfire.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Forest Watchers are also tasked with protecting the ecosystem. Recently, potentially because of the Withering Zones, the alligators have become... shall we say, unusually manic."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Not only have they been invading other animals' territories, but they're reproducing at a faster rate. If this goes on, they won't just be a danger to the children, but to the forest's ecosystem as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "#Luckily, your opponent isn't a Withering Zone this time. It's my time to shine, hehe. You rest up, {NICKNAME}, leave this one to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll come help you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Rest? Not a chance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're coming to help too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Is it really okay...? That's great then, I'll finally get to fight side by side with you!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7300213": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Rana",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Here we are. When I was little, I would often take this road to go down to the river valley to play."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "The Withering Zones are appearing so quickly now, and Tighnari and the others are too busy to deal with them in time. But it's a good thing we have you here now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Leave it to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rana",
                    "T": "Okay! You made clean work of those Withering Zones before, but they're still dangerous. If it gets to be too much, be sure to leave the realm and take some rest."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
